  "description": "Damaged, sparse, haunting. A reef that has suffered thermal stress and lost most of its inhabitants. Only a sine fundamental remains, dark and ringing through skeletal resonance. Second source has died. Heavy reverb fills the emptiness. The parasite is still there, slowly finishing the job. Journey Mode means this elegy plays out over minutes. Hit State Reset to attempt recovery.",
